       <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Scope&lt;/b&gt; — which objects Smart Bake analyzes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Auto (Whole Scene)&lt;/b&gt; (default) — scans every mesh/empty/armature in the scene and bakes only the ones actually driven by a constraint, IK, driver, or blend-shape driver.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Selected&lt;/b&gt; — restricts the scan to the current selection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
